<section id="how" class="section">
  <div class="how">
    <div class="how-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow-mono">How it works</div>
      <h2 class="sec-title">You describe the outcome. Your agents handle the rest.</h2>
      <p class="sec-lead">No prompts to engineer, no tools to wire up by hand. Brief Houston the way you'd brief a new hire, then watch the work move across the board.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step reveal reveal-d1">
        <div class="step-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.1 2.1 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4z"/></svg></div>
        <div>
          <h3>Tell it what you need.</h3>
          <p>Describe the job in plain language, like "keep our invoices reconciled" or "book me six sales calls a week." Houston turns it into a mission.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal reveal-d2">
        <div class="step-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="3.2"/><path d="M2.5 20a6.5 6.5 0 0 1 13 0"/><path d="M17 7h5M19.5 4.5v5"/></svg></div>
        <div>
          <h3>Hire the agents for it.</h3>
          <p>Pick a specialist from the store or build your own. Each agent gets its own memory, its own tools, and access to only what you allow.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal reveal-d3">
        <div class="step-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.5V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h9"/><path d="M2 9h20"/><path d="m16 18 2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
        <div>
          <h3>Watch the work get done.</h3>
          <p>Tasks move across your mission board in real time, on the apps you already use. Step in when you want, ignore it when you don't.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
